ockquote><blockquote>正常嚟講唔會<br />\nbb體內有enzyme分解乳糖</blockquote><br />\n咁點解我哋依家冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n飲奶肚痾主要係因為人體消化唔到牛奶中的乳糖<br />\n未消化嘅乳糖會被腸道細菌消化<br />\n細菌消化乳糖過程會嚴重刺激腸<br />\n導致肚痾<br />\n而bb體內有分解乳糖嘅酶(enzyme)<br />\n所以唔會肚痾<br />\n但大部份人(特別係亞洲人)長大後都會漸漸失去生產呢隻酶嘅能力<br />\n所以先會肚瀉<br />\n<br />\n你google乳糖不耐症 會有更詳細解釋"},{"pid":"7ead3dc4ce8507605dd02cf7ff6a07248d1e64cc","tid":406262,"uid":60115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T15:03:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>正常嚟講唔會<br />\nbb體內有enzyme分解乳糖</blockquote><br />\n咁點解我哋依家冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n成年人都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n只有少量人有"},{"pid":"99fadf883555662e54e913824dd1a4d40144d873","tid":406262,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T15:11:08.000Z","msg":"牛奶唔同人奶<br />\n人緊係瘋狂飲人奶"},{"pid":"24877b5cdeb2ea59461dc5660fddb06dc170d43c","tid":406262,"uid":20224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T18:28:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>牛奶唔同人奶<br />\n人緊係瘋狂飲人奶</blockquote><br />\n係都我飲先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89f674b4493147b5a54c858aa535f18212cd7e16","tid":406262,"uid":38017,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T00:09:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>牛奶唔同人奶<br />\n人緊係瘋狂飲人奶</blockquote><br />\n係都我飲先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n認真 有得餵人奶就最好餵人奶 個b會聰明啲"},{"pid":"7017ccb2418a318e32c1c1648d5bf34686bb873a","tid":406262,"uid":20224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T01:37:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>牛奶唔同人奶<br />\n人緊係瘋狂飲人奶</blockquote><br />\n係都我飲先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n認真 有得餵人奶就最好餵人奶 個b會聰明啲